In order to perform the correctly training process for gait authentication, please follow the instructions below:

 - When you start the process, please do not perform any other activity other than walking;
 - Ensure the surface is plain and there is no front steps;
 - Walk as naturally as possible, keeping the same rhythm;
 - Do not hold the device in your hands, rather keep it as close as possible to your body;
 - The process ends whenever you hear a sound signal and you see a screen message.

 It takes 5minutes.
